  ((SELECT id FROM mock_test_bank WHERE exam_type = 'TOPIK_I' AND test_number = 52 ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 1), 'listening', 19, '남자 :(걱정하는 목소리로)미영 씨,왜 그래요?어디 안 좋아요?
