  ((SELECT id FROM mock_test_bank WHERE exam_type = 'TOPIK_I' AND test_number = 52 ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 1), 'listening', 21, '여자 :(감탄하며)와,집에 만화책이 정말 많네요.
